rows.label: tev910601_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev910601_SEL0020
rows.name: Ask him what he's doing there.

rows.label: tev910601_MSG0030
rows.name: ...I'm sorry, do I know you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910601_MSG0040
rows.name:
If you need something, I'm sure one of
Grenada's grunts will be more than happy
to assist you. I haven't the inclination.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910601_JNK0050
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev910601_SEL0060
rows.name: Ask how he's been doing lately.

rows.label: tev910601_MSG0070
rows.name:
Why on God's green earth
would I answer that?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910601_MSG0080
rows.name:
You may be a BLADE, but I do not owe
you my time and energy. Be aware that
I have Secretary Nagi on speed-dial...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910601_JNK0090
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: tev910601_SEL0100
rows.name: Ask him about Liesel.

rows.label: tev910601_MSG0110
rows.name:
Liesel has qualified to be our test pilot
after passing Grenada's rigorous gauntlet
of tests. Her performance was exemplary.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910601_MSG0120
rows.name:
The real problem is that she continues to
overstep her authority. It shows a lack of
regard for her proper place in the system.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910601_MSG0130
rows.name:
The impertinence, I swear...
Snotty-nosed, boorish little upstart...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910601_JNK0140
rows.name: Discuss

rows.label: tev910601_SEL0150
rows.name: Ask him about the Hraesvelg.

rows.label: tev910601_MSG0160
rows.name:
I'm sure I don't need to spell this
out for you, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910601_MSG0170
rows.name:
The information you've gained about the
Hraesvelg isn't yet public, and covered by
the strictest NDA known to man or alien.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910601_MSG0180
rows.name:
If I catch wind of so much as a peep, the
repercussions will be as onerous as they
will be appropriateâ€”I'll make sure of it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev910601_MSG0190
rows.name: Cancel

rows.label: tev910601_MSG0200
rows.name: Cancel
